	   <tr><td colspan=2>Using the foraged item, when you get the message "are you sure you want to drop this" leave that message box up.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's annoying because it is in the middle of the screen, but it will change when you click on the trigger.<br><br><br>One note- I found Tanik on my third try with this method, and he was not on the ramp.  If facing Kael from the top of the ramp, he was to the right a fair distance.  I had also charmed a rabbit to serve as a pet to point me in the right direction of the trigger.  When I would get frustrated, I'd move the pet to a new spot to see if I was still going in the right direction.<br><br>Also, after I found the KromDS, I'd re-sow and and trigger them in the hopes of getting a Tanik trigger spawn the next time.<br><br>Hope this helps.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
